amelia is a 2009 canadian-american biographical film about the life of amelia earhart . the film was directed by mira nair and starred hilary swank as earhart and richard gere as her husband , george putnam . the cast list also included christopher eccleston and ewan mcgregor . most of the story is told in flashbacks before ending with earhart 's mysterious disappearance . the film was written by ronald bass and anna hamilton phelan , using research from sources including east to the dawn by susan butler and the sound of wings by mary s. lovell . the film has garnered predominantly negative reviews .